data.description: SPRAWLING 3 BDR. 2 BATH RANCH HOME  with NICE CURB APPEAL features 1900 Sq.Ft. of LIVING SPACE all on ONE LEVEL. The SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM has a DOUBLE SIDED FIREPLACE w/RECESS LIGHTING,and a NEW LARGE COVE MOLDING &  BOW WINDOW 6/23 along with NEW DRYWALL, CHAIR RAIL & LIGHTING FIXTURES. BEAUTIFUL HARDWOOD FLOORS run THOUGH-OUT most of the HOME. The RAISED DOOR MAPLE CABINET KITCHEN w/CUSTOM CERAMIC TILE FLOOR overlooks the DINING ROOM w/FIREPLACE & SLIDING DOORS to a NEWLY CARPETED ENCLOSED SCREEN PORCH to the PRIVACY FENCED YARD w/Shed.. Off the kitchen is a LAUNDRY ROOM W/LARGE PANTRY CLOSET and WASHER & DRYER. There are three GOOD SIZE BEDROOMS W/ LARGE CLOSETS. two being DOUBLE CLOSETS. ROOF 5yrs. NEWER, FURNACE & CENTRAL AIR. 4' Concrete crawl, LEAF GUARD GUTTERS Too!.
